{"tid":412252,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日...吃了...","createTime":"2017-09-24T13:26:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T05:28:49.000Z","uid":64259,"like":17,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ce52326aa9896c28ed838fbdbfa917ebaaaeac28","tid":412252,"uid":64259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T13:26:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3996b3901d13ed8c036c2326246ff6d077936feb","tid":412252,"uid":71166,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T13:31:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[member]<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/211226_fa8d9aff014bf9530d93306f0e8ca220.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F211226_fa8d9aff014bf9530d93306f0e8ca220.jpg&h=b371cadd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一站黎到荃灣<br />\n大廚xx 韓式炸雞粒 $30<br />\n好撚嫩滑 正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二站...<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/211430_848b4944724e5be1ee4a943f4ffe40c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F211430_848b4944724e5be1ee4a943f4ffe40c0.jpg&h=d05be6c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n落少少 去左食5蚊豆花<br />\n操你媽的b 5蚊屌打曬全港豆花<br />\n芝麻糊既襯托下<br />\n糖都唔洗落！<br />\n<br />\n第三站...<br />\n我屌 間彩虹吐司執7左 嬲<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/211625_f3481e79112dd6904ea159019f81ce10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F211625_f3481e79112dd6904ea159019f81ce10.jpg&h=3135a2fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好...過斜對面食9蚊喪辣沙嗲汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第四站<br />\n日式q餅<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/211847_49172f3dc622a68beebbc668519ef441.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F211847_49172f3dc622a68beebbc668519ef441.jpg&h=307f462d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我靠 好脆喔<br />\n超屌的拉絲 配上 司華洋腸<br />\n加上沙律汁 辣粉<br />\n超巨型的！<br />\n<br />\n第五站 人排我又排...<br />\n沛xxx<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/212013_4cf056b999485b3081dc63a914af8ae4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F212013_4cf056b999485b3081dc63a914af8ae4.jpg&h=384e1271&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢到9蚊<br />\n11層蛋糕 窮撚食2件就頂到半日<br />\nd cream多到...<br />\n<br />\n第六站<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/212136_745ba62199b0048a30109c62bc8edb28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F212136_745ba62199b0048a30109c62bc8edb28.jpg&h=92010942&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n串燒...成條野似關東煮咁 不介紹了<br />\n<br />\n第7站<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/212226_6c5b8e72c45ca2fc934f70af86323ecc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F212226_6c5b8e72c45ca2fc934f70af86323ecc.jpg&h=8f8e417e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不介紹了 好普通<br />\n<br />\n跟住你老豆置羅漢 我直入元朗<br />\n<br />\n第8站 b仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/212326_3dc4cc970c8489035ff1f8a0a7ba3902.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F212326_3dc4cc970c8489035ff1f8a0a7ba3902.jpg&h=ac771e79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁就17蚊 無以前咁辣喇<br />\n我食左咁多次 都覺得有落好多糖..<br />\n<br />\n第9站 埋去叫聲肥姐先<br />\n肥姐 黎雙飛 走茜 堂食！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/212446_08d72ed2152f25396c6dedaa9b1baec3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F212446_08d72ed2152f25396c6dedaa9b1baec3.jpg&h=bd69c862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n肥姐 你..好肥美（d蠔）<br />\n<br />\n第10站 作為港男<br />\n買返半打恆香老婆餅畀老味食先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (無圖）<br />\n<br />\n多謝大家收睇 <br />\n完<br />\n[/mmber]</blockquote>"},{"pid":"8266bc9016a5e666f09f7c13c114d463999c44d0","tid":412252,"uid":53652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T13:32:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大食 岩我"},{"pid":"d03840ba6963688e7ca3e3bbbae20b62a1fa3788","tid":412252,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T13:36:45.000Z","msg":"正野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1733f4a81b595ec5f6992465a649fe6cd1e746f4","tid":412252,"uid":30642,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T13:38:00.000Z","msg":"真係乜都放上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89781981cca3f4affcfeb40a653dc63af508894b","tid":412252,"uid":64259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T13:38:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大食 岩我</blockquote><br />\n邊忽大食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日全日食呢d"},{"pid":"45a3d414bdaabf689ec77074dfb5a5a3ba1c8d83","tid":412252,"uid":64259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T13:39:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 還可以喔～～～<br />\n謝謝您<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd681a011f2e84f87a65a6979f8402efdfea87c4","tid":412252,"uid":64259,"like":4,"dislike":0